Tout le matériel est fourni — il vous suffit d''apporter votre créativité et vous repartirez avec un pareo unique, réalisé de vos propres mains. Une expérience', 'A hands-on pareu painting experience in Raiatea', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/lamedupareu.jpg', NULL, 'lornapitovai@gmail.com', '+689 87376668', 'PK30.9 C/mer - Motu Nuutere', 'French Polynesia', 'Arts & Culture', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2025-11-27 07:23:16.513022+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Vaihere Pito', '{English,French,Tahitian}', '{"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@vaiohani", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/100046471642888", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/pareubyvaiohani.00"}', 'Tumaraa', 'Raiatea', 'Ils Sous Le Vent', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Lame%20Du%20Pareu.png', 'French Polynesia', false, NULL, NULL, 'l-ame-du-pareu-by-vai-ohani', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('20b54ac1-50ae-4475-89ef-b50569505408', 'M.Steven', 'This artist brings worlds to life through intricate, hand-drawn line work, creating pieces that feel both deeply personal and endlessly expansive. Every artwork is built stroke by stroke — layering symbols, creatures, and flowing forms that invite the viewer to slow down and discover something new each time they look.

Inspired by storytelling, movement, and the complexity of lived experience, their work blends fine detail with raw expression. Using acrylic paint and acrylic pen alongside traditional drawing tools, each piece carries its own rhythm — reflecting patience, discipline, and a deep respect for the creative process.

Beyond visual art, this same care and creativity extend into handcrafted desserts and custom celebration cakes, including wedding and birthday designs. Whether expressed on paper, canvas, or through edible art, the artist approaches every creation with the same intention: balance, beauty, and meaning.

These works are never rushed — they are thoughtfully crafted, allowing ideas to unfold naturally. The result is a body of work that feels alive and grounded, celebrating creativity as a form of meditation, expression, and connection across many mediums.', 'Stories in Every Intricate Stroke & Sweet Creation', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/msteven.jpeg', NULL, 'mariosteven75@yahoo.co.nz', NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Arts & Culture', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2025-12-14 08:18:01.195186+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Mario Steven', '{Fijian,Rotuman,Hindi,"Te Reo Māori (basic)",English}', '{"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@m.stevenfjrot23"}', NULL, 'New Zealand', 'New Zealand', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/M%20Steven.png', 'Fiji, Italy', false, NULL, NULL, 'm-steven', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('464afb2e-e877-458d-a6cb-d0b0e6dd049d', 'The Artwork of Dave Sotogi', 'Dave Sotogi is a New Zealand artist whose work brings the heart of the Pacific to life through rich symbolism, cultural depth, and emotive portraiture. His paintings blend modern artistry with ancestral influence, honouring the beauty, strength, and stories of Pacific people.

From striking portraits to symbolic, nature-inspired works, each piece reflects Dave''s deep connection to heritage, identity, and the lands and waters that shape us. His art captures moments of reflection, power, and serenity — inviting viewers to feel, remember, and connect.

Today, Dave''s work is celebrated in homes across Aotearoa and around the world, available as premium canvas prints and carefully crafted wall art. Every creation carries a story, a spirit, and a sense of belonging — an invitation to experience Pacific art through a contemporary lens.', 'Contemporary Maori Art in Motion', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/dave.jpg', 'https://desotogi.co.nz', 'info@desotogi.co.nz', NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Arts & Culture', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2025-12-12 18:55:24.793631+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Dave Sotogi', '{English}', '{"facebook": "https://facebook.com/desotogi", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/desotogi"}', NULL, 'Christchurch', 'South Island', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Dave.png', 'New Zealand Māori', false, NULL, NULL, 'the-artwork-of-dave-sotogi', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('f9ba8226-cffa-44af-9481-0bcfbd86c100', 'DAN KAS Construction', 'Dan Kas Construction is an Auckland-based building company built on hard work, attention to detail, and a genuine commitment to quality workmanship. Led by a skilled Samoan crew, the team brings values of service, care, and collective strength into every project, delivering work with integrity and pride.

Specialising in new builds, renovations, decking, fencing, recladding, and general maintenance, Dan Kas Construction provides reliable, well-crafted solutions designed to last. Each project is approached with a focus on durability, functionality, and clean, professional finishes, ensuring results that are both practical and visually appealing.

Known throughout Auckland for their strong work ethic, clear communication, and fair, competitive pricing, the team works closely with clients to make every build a collaborative and stress-free experience. Client ideas are respected and combined with expert guidance to achieve outcomes that balance vision with craftsmanship.

More than just construction, Dan Kas Construction is about building long-term relationships and creating homes and structures that support families and communities. Whether upgrading an existing space or starting a new build, the team brings precision, reliability, and Pacific heart to every stage of the journey.', 'Built on Trust, Crafted by Community', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/dankas.png', 'https://dan-kas-construction.nz', 'pacificmarketltd@gmail.com', '021 0887 8365', NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Construction & Trades', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-06 18:27:30.26066+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-01-06', 'Dan Kas', '{English}', '{"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@dan.kas7", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/dan.kas.construction"}', NULL, 'Auckland', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Dan%20Kas.png', 'Samoa', false, NULL, NULL, 'dan-kas-construction', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('8e3c51fd-f7f9-4873-a91e-5edafb7b10f0', 'Inailau', 'Inailau Business Women''s Network is a community-driven platform dedicated to uplifting, connecting, and empowering Pacific women in business.

Rooted in collaboration and collective growth, Inailau creates safe, supportive spaces where women can share knowledge, build confidence, and grow both personally and professionally. Through networking events, workshops, mentoring sessions, and global connections, Inailau supports Pacific women entrepreneurs at every stage of their journey — from early ideas to established businesses.

