Strengthen the Pacific digital economy.', 'Digital products for freelancers, creators, and small businesses', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/saasycookies.png', 'https://www.saasycookies.com', 'saasycookies@gmail.com', NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Digital Media & Technology', 'active', 'verified', 'd5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4', NULL, '2025-11-27 05:54:58.04014+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2025-11-27', 'Jasmin Benioni', '{English,French}', '{"tiktok": "", "facebook": "", "linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/111610220", "instagram": ""}', NULL, 'Auckland', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/SaaSy%20Cookies.png', 'Cook Islands, French Polynesia', true, '2026-02-26 22:33:27.633401+00', 'system', 'saasy-cookies', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('53d84963-82c7-40e1-92f8-8f9f7d06f2c5', 'Pacifikmarket.nc', 'Pacifikmarket.nc is a vibrant Pacific-led platform based in Nouvelle-Calédonie, dedicated to celebrating, showcasing, and uplifting Pacific designers, artisans, and creative talent from across the region.

More than a marketplace, Pacifikmarket.nc is a cultural movement — bringing together fashion shows, artisan markets, creative collaborations, and community events that highlight the richness, diversity, and contemporary expression of Pacific identity. From traditional craftsmanship to modern Pacific fashion, each piece and event tells a story of heritage, pride, and innovation.

Pacifikmarket.nc creates meaningful opportunities for Pacific creatives to be seen, supported, and celebrated — locally and internationally — while building strong connections between cultures, generations, and islands.

Through fashion, storytelling, and community-driven events, Pacifikmarket.nc continues to amplify Pacific voices and create spaces where culture thrives.', 'Kanak and Pasifika Designs', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/pacifikmarketnc.png', NULL, 'pacifikmarket.nc@gmail.com', '(+687) 798854', NULL, 'French Polynesia', 'Arts & Culture', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2025-12-16 02:55:48.501002+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Christiane Waneissi', '{French,English,Spanish}', '{"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@pacifikmarket_nc", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/Pacifikmarketnc", "linkedin": "https://linkedin.com/company/pacifikmarket-nc", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/pacifikmarket.nc_newcaledonia"}', NULL, 'Noumea', 'New Caledonia', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Pacifik%20Market.png', 'New Caledonia', false, NULL, NULL, 'pacifikmarket-nc', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('46d354a9-f6db-43d9-9527-4e0aa8b9820e', 'Da Utah Taro Leaf Man', 'Da Utah Taro Leaf Man bridges Hawaiʻi and Utah by delivering fresh, island-grown taro leaves straight to families who crave the real thing.

We know that taro leaves aren''t just ingredients — they''re tradition, celebration, and identity. That''s why we source directly from Hawaiʻi farms and ship weekly to ensure freshness and quality you can trust.

This isn''t just produce.
This is culture in a bag.', 'From Our Farms to Your Arms', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/taroleafman.jpg', 'https://alohainutah.org/', 'send@mail.pacificmarket.co.nz', '+1 801 318 4972', NULL, 'United States', 'Food & Beverage', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2026-02-23 21:49:50.314899+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'SENGA NUGA-TUIMASEVE', '{English}', '{}', NULL, 'Utah', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/taroleaf.png', NULL, false, NULL, NULL, 'da-utah-taro-leaf-man', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('74845da6-e0b1-421c-8181-7e6753c152f9', 'Zeena Khan Coaching', 'Zeena Khan Coaching stands at the intersection of modern leadership and cultural wisdom, offering a nuanced approach to professional development.

With a focus on empowering leaders to build agile and confident teams, Zeena''s coaching practice is particularly attuned to the complexities of the AI era. Her methodology is grounded in a strengths-based framework that encourages individuals to harness their unique capabilities while remaining culturally aware.

Zeena Khan brings a wealth of experience to her coaching engagements, drawing from her own heritage and understanding of diverse cultural perspectives. This blend of insight ensures that her clients are not only prepared to meet the challenges of today''s fast-paced business environment but are also equipped to lead with empathy and respect for the diverse backgrounds within their teams.

At the core of Zeena''s practice is the belief that true leadership is about fostering an environment where all team members can thrive. By emphasizing cultural awareness and personal strengths, she helps leaders create workplaces that are both innovative and inclusive. Zeena Khan Coaching is dedicated to nurturing leadership that is as dynamic as the world around us, with a commitment to guiding professionals towards their highest potential.', 'Empowering leaders to foster agile, confident teams in the AI era.', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/zeena.jpg', 'https://www.zeenakhan.com', 'hello@zeenakhan.com', '021364881', NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Consulting & Professional Services', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-17 23:14:01.458139+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Zeena Khan', '{Hindi,English}', '{"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@ZeenaKhanCoaching", "youtube": "https://youtube.com/@Adaptability Advantage", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/ZeenaKhanCoaching"}', NULL, 'Auckland', 'North Island', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Zeena.png', 'Fiji, China, India', false, NULL, NULL, 'zeena-khan-coaching', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('c9fc68e6-da63-4def-9d0b-13991ddc3926', 'Te Mauri o te Makawe', 'Nuku te manaaki, nuku te manaaki, ka ora ai te iwi.
With your support and my support, our community will thrive.

My name is Iesha Te-Iho. I am a qualified barber, creative, and proud Waiuku local. My journey here was not a straight line — but every challenge sharpened my purpose and showed me that barbering could be more than a trade. It could be a doorway to healing.

From that understanding, Te Mauri o te Makawe: The Koha Manawa was born.

This kaupapa delivers professional grooming and braiding through a mobile service, reaching people and places often overlooked — hospices, spinal units, rehabilitation centres, and rural communities where transport and access are barriers. But this work is about far more than hair.

Through whakahoki te tapu, hair is treated with care and respectfully returned to Papatūānuku using traditional tikanga — uku (clay), harakeke (flax), and korowai — protecting the mana of our whānau. Alongside this, kōrero is shared and recorded, preserving the voices, stories, and heartbeat of the community.

This kaupapa began with one chair and one set of tools, but the vision is a Waka Wānanga — a collective of skilled creatives travelling across Aotearoa and beyond, delivering workshops, teaching tikanga, uplifting hauora, and restoring identity through creativity.

At its heart, this is about legacy. About building something that lasts — not just 100 years, but for generations — by caring for people, culture, and community, together.', 'Any Style. Any Hair. Any Where.', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/temauri.jpg', 'https://msha.ke/beauty_withinyou', 'hairwithesha@gmail.com', '02102965229', NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Health & Wellness', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2025-12-01 08:40:49.119488+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Iesha Rawinia', '{English}', '{"facebook": "https://facebook.com/TeKohaManawa", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/tekohamanawa"}', NULL, 'Auckland', 'Auckland', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Te%20Mauri.png', 'Cook Islands, New Zealand Māori', false, NULL, NULL, 'te-mauri-o-te-makawe', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('e0e03cd4-3a8b-48f9-8ffa-546abfa7925c', 'SenseAI', 'SenseAI is a supportive space for your thoughts, feelings, and ideas — without judgment, pressure, or noise.

Life can be complex, and sometimes you just need help making sense of what''s in your head. SenseAI blends journaling with compassionate AI guidance to help you reflect, gain perspective, and move forward with confidence.

It''s like having a thoughtful companion who listens, understands, and helps you see things more clearly.', 'AI-Powered Journaling App - Type It, Speak It, Scan It', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/senseai.png', 'https://www.senseai.co.nz', 'msbenioni+1@gmail.com', NULL, NULL, 'New Zealand', 'Digital Media & Technology', 'active', 'featured_plus', 'd5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4', NULL, '2026-02-07 18:26:40.653265+00', '2026-03-03 06:13:06.643013+00', '2026-02-26', 'Jasmin Benioni', '{English}', '{}', NULL, 'Auckland', 'Auckland', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/SenseAI.png', 'Cook Islands, French Polynesia', true, '2026-02-28 02:32:15.586966+00', 'system', 'senseai', false, NULL, NULL, false, 'none'),
	('c4530355-c5fb-47fb-ac89-07574831f9e7', 'Avalon Wellness and Performance', 'Avalon Wellness & Performance is a holistic health clinic dedicated to helping people move better, feel stronger, and live with greater ease and confidence. Through personalised, hands-on care, Avalon supports recovery, long-term wellness, and peak physical performance.

The clinic takes an integrative approach to treatment, combining techniques such as Active Release Technique (ART), Osteopathic Manual Therapy, Cranial Sacral Therapy, and therapeutic massage. Each session is tailored to the individual, addressing not only symptoms but the underlying causes of pain, tension, and movement restrictions.

At Avalon, the body is viewed as a connected system. Treatment plans are developed through careful assessment and collaboration, ensuring care aligns with each client''s goals — whether that''s injury recovery, pain management, improved mobility, or enhanced athletic performance.

Avalon Wellness & Performance provides a calm, professional environment where expertise and compassion come together. From deep tissue and mobility-focused work to gentle therapies that support nervous system balance and stress relief, every session is delivered with intention and care.

More than treatment, Avalon empowers clients with the tools, support, and knowledge needed to maintain their wellbeing long after their session ends — helping them move forward feeling stronger, balanced, and supported.', 'Move Better. Feel Better. Live Better.', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/avalon.jpg', 'https://www.avalonwellnessandperformance.com/', 'avalonwellnessperformance@gmail.com', '+632394274697', '10661 Airport Pulling Road N #10, Naples FL 34109', 'United States', 'Health & Wellness', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-08 00:54:56.222151+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Avalon Wellness Performance', '{English}', '{"twitter": "https://twitter.com/WellnessAvalon", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/avalonwellnessandperformance", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/avalonwellnessandperformance"}', 'Naples', 'Naples', 'FL', '34109', NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Avalon.png', NULL, false, NULL, NULL, 'avalon-wellness-and-performance', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('9ab9b40a-101a-4afe-a9f2-c17f9b616e87', 'VAHINE CHIC', 'Vahine Chic is a celebration of Polynesian artistry — handmade creations crafted with patience, passion, and the timeless beauty of our islands.

From their home in Tahiti, each piece is made with love, blending vibrant colours, natural textures, and traditional inspiration to honour the spirit of Fenua. Their work reflects more than craftsmanship; it carries stories of family, culture, and connection.

Whether it''s a lovingly woven accessory or a delicately detailed piece of décor, every item invites you to discover the treasures of Fenua and the warmth of the people who create them.

At Vahine Chic, artistry is not just a skill — it is a way of sharing joy. A way of keeping culture alive. A way of bringing a little piece of paradise into everyday life.', 'Made In Tahiti', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/vahine.jpg', NULL, 'pacificmarketltd@gmail.com', '89 54 32 68', 'Marche de Papeete, pres de l''escalator (Papeete Market - near the escalator)', 'French Polynesia', 'Arts & Culture', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2025-12-11 22:41:59.920616+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Timeri Pollock', '{French}', '{"facebook": "https://facebook.com/Artisantchic"}', 'Papeete', 'Tahiti', 'Tahiti', NULL, '10am - 2pm 
10h00 - 14h00', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Vahine.png', 'French Polynesia', false, NULL, NULL, 'vahine-chic', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('cc214a50-bbbb-4a98-9c77-feb1899c1cae', 'Mana Carvings', 'Mana Carvings is a celebration of Cook Islands heritage, storytelling, and craftsmanship. Every piece — whether carved on wood, engraved on drinkware, or designed for the home — carries deep cultural meaning, ancestral patterns, and the spirit of mana.

Each artwork is handcrafted with precision and intention, transforming traditional motifs into modern, functional pieces that honour identity and connection. From symbolic creatures to intricate Polynesian designs, every creation holds a story — one that reflects culture, legacy, and the pride of the Pacific.

Made with heart and guided by tradition, Mana Carvings exists to keep our stories alive, one handcrafted design at a time.', 'Handcrafted with Culture, Carved with Mana', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/manacarving.jpg', NULL, 'manacarvings@gmail.com', NULL, NULL, 'Australia', 'Arts & Culture', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2025-12-12 17:30:11.143898+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-02-26', 'Kai Strickland', '{English}', '{"facebook": "https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=61577910021592", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/manacarvings"}', NULL, 'Sydney', 'NSW', NULL, NULL, 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Mana.png', 'Cook Islands', false, NULL, NULL, 'mana-carvings', false, NULL, NULL, true, 'homepage'),
	('ce4a274e-c94d-475f-988e-23741f9e58c5', 'Rebalance Qi Acupuncture', 'Rebalance Qi Acupuncture is a calming and supportive clinic
