	('ebbc9e74-75cc-4b8f-808a-4798ab5e1afd', 'NAUNA', 'Nauna is a vibrant creative and cultural brand based in Apia, Samoa, celebrated for its authentic elei fashion and Pacific-inspired designs. Rooted in Samoan artistry and storytelling, Nauna showcases clothing and creative expressions that reflect contemporary Pacific identity while honouring traditional patterns and aesthetics.

Known for its bold, beautiful pieces and strong community engagement, Nauna has built a dedicated following by blending island heritage with modern style, making traditional influences accessible and wearable for everyday life. Whether through fashion, creative content, or collaborations with local artists, Nauna is a cultural voice that elevates Pacific design and celebrates Samoan creative excellence.', 'Authentic Elei - Made in Samoa', 'https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/nauna.webp', 'https://linktr.ee/nauna_', 'nauna_@outlook.com', '+6857539518', 'Fugalei  (Vaai Compound)', 'Samoa', 'Arts & Culture', 'active', 'verified', NULL, NULL, '2026-01-05 03:06:07.035478+00', '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00', '2026-01-05', 'Adriana Kamu', '{English}', '{"facebook": "https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=61564135313244", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/nauna.samoa"}', NULL, 'Apia', 'Samoa', NULL, 'Mon/Friday: 8am - 5pm
