is specific weaving tradition:\r\n\r\nNorth Solomon (Buka)\r\nSouthern Highlands\r\nEastern Highlands\r\n\r\nThese handcrafted pieces are both functional and meaningful, suitable for home décor, shopping, picnics, and baby carrying — while carrying the stories, skills, and heritage of the communities who make them.\r\n\r\nBy supporting Papua New Guinea Bilums & Baskets, you are helping preserve traditional knowledge and create income opportunities for PNG artisans.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Linah Mountford", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"facebook": "https://facebook.com/PapuaNewGuineaBilumsAndBasketsCjLjMountford", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/pngbilumsnbaskets"}, "state_region": "Queensland", "contact_email": "Cmford@southernphone.com.au", "contact_phone": "0423 819 378", "business_hours": "10am to 2pm", "contact_website": null, "languages_spoken": ["Pidgin"], "cultural_identity": "Papua New Guinean, Papua New Guinean", "short_description": "CJ & LJ Mountford", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-26 21:10:10.394806+00'),
	('36377b05-973a-4ae2-91db-d8a740451462', 'businesses', '70ea5ff4-fe63-4d3e-b526-cfa3ec0dc95a', 'UPDATE', '{"id": "70ea5ff4-fe63-4d3e-b526-cfa3ec0dc95a", "city": "Draper", "name": "Warrior Lines Tattoo", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": "12233 900 E", "claimed": false, "country": "United States", "user_id": "d5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4", "featured": true, "industry": "Culture & Heritage", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771900321960.jpg", "verified": true, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771900497365.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2025-12-17T04:52:57.713415+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-26T20:51:09.463207+00:00", "description": "Warrior Lines Tattoo is a veteran-owned tattoo studio built on discipline, respect, and the belief that great art comes from a strong, healthy environment.\r\n\r\nWe specialise in bold black and grey work, custom designs, and Polynesian-inspired tattoos that carry meaning, structure, and story.\r\n\r\nThis is a no-nonsense shop for artists and clients who value integrity, craftsmanship, and authenticity. We reject ego, drama, and gatekeeping, and instead foster a space where artists are encouraged to grow, sharpen their skills, and take pride in their work — without judgment or pressure.\r\n\r\nAt Warrior Lines Tattoo, tattooing is more than ink. It''s commitment. It''s brotherhood. It''s honouring the past while building something stronger for the future — one line at a time.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Hans Bennion", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@tribal_touch", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/tribaltouchdesigns"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "hans@warriorlines.com", "contact_phone": "4843797885", "business_hours": "By Appointment Only", "contact_website": "https://www.warriorlines.com", "languages_spoken": ["Fijian", "Tongan", "Samoan"], "cultural_identity": "Samoa, Tonga, Fiji", "short_description": "Polynesian-inspired Art and Tattoo Studio", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', '{"id": "70ea5ff4-fe63-4d3e-b526-cfa3ec0dc95a", "city": "Draper", "name": "Warrior Lines Tattoo", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": "12233 900 E", "claimed": true, "country": "United States", "user_id": "d5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4", "featured": true, "industry": "Culture & Heritage", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771900321960.jpg", "verified": true, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771900497365.png", "claimed_at": "2026-02-26T21:10:10.394806+00:00", "claimed_by": "system", "created_at": "2025-12-17T04:52:57.713415+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-26T21:10:10.394806+00:00", "description": "Warrior Lines Tattoo is a veteran-owned tattoo studio built on discipline, respect, and the belief that great art comes from a strong, healthy environment.\r\n\r\nWe specialise in bold black and grey work, custom designs, and Polynesian-inspired tattoos that carry meaning, structure, and story.\r\n\r\nThis is a no-nonsense shop for artists and clients who value integrity, craftsmanship, and authenticity. We reject ego, drama, and gatekeeping, and instead foster a space where artists are encouraged to grow, sharpen their skills, and take pride in their work — without judgment or pressure.\r\n\r\nAt Warrior Lines Tattoo, tattooing is more than ink. It''s commitment. It''s brotherhood. It''s honouring the past while building something stronger for the future — one line at a time.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Hans Bennion", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@tribal_touch", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/tribaltouchdesigns"}, "state_regio