ief and renewed\r\nenergy.", "postal_code": "2025", "contact_name": "Sandy Suriyachaik", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"facebook": "https://facebook.com/rebalanceqi.acupuncture", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/rebalanceqi.acupuncture"}, "state_region": "Auckland", "contact_email": "info@rebalanceqi.co.nz", "contact_phone": "022 388 5718", "business_hours": "Monday - 9:30am-6:30pm\r\nTuesday - Closed\r\nWednesday\t9:30am-6:30pm\r\nThursday - Closed\r\nFriday - 9:30am-2pm\r\nSaturday - 8am-12pm\r\nSunday - Closed", "contact_website": "https://www.rebalanceqi.co.nz", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": null, "short_description": "Restore, Renew, Rebalance.", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-26 22:40:17.692594+00'),
	('51b502be-8f05-464c-9a5d-2cc087ae5433', 'businesses', 'fa253572-ef34-4f2b-8ea1-11293b37b492', 'DELETE', '{"id": "fa253572-ef34-4f2b-8ea1-11293b37b492", "city": "Draper", "name": "Warrior Lines Tattoo ", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": "12233 900 E", "claimed": true, "country": "US", "user_id": "d5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4", "featured": true, "industry": "Culture & Heritage", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771900321960.jpg", "verified": true, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771900497365.png", "claimed_at": "2026-02-26T22:33:27.633401+00:00", "claimed_by": "system", "created_at": "2025-12-17T04:52:57.713415+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-24T02:35:04.618912+00:00", "description": "<p><strong>Warrior Lines Tattoo</strong> is a veteran-owned tattoo studio built on discipline, respect, and the belief that great art comes from a strong, healthy environment.<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Open Sans Fallback&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Open Sans Fallback&quot;, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Open Sans Fallback&quot;, sans-serif;\">We specialise in bold black and grey work, custom designs, and Polynesian-inspired tattoos that carry meaning, structure, and story.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Open Sans Fallback&quot;, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p>\n<p>This is a no-nonsense shop for artists and clients who value integrity, craftsmanship, and authenticity. We reject ego, drama, and gatekeeping, and instead foster a space where artists are encouraged to grow, sharpen their skills, and take pride in their work — without judgment or pressure.</p><p><br></p>\n<p>At Warrior Lines Tattoo, tattooing is more than ink. It’s commitment. It’s brotherhood. It’s honouring the past while building something stronger for the future — one line at a time.</p>", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Hans Bennion", "created_date": "2025-12-17", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@tribal_touch", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/tribaltouchdesigns"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "hans@warriorlines.com", "contact_phone": "4843797885", "business_hours": "By Appointment Only", "contact_website": "https://www.warriorlines.com", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Other, Samoa", "short_description": "Polynesian-inspired Art and Tattoo Studio", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-26 22:41:04.690001+00'),
	('cf4082e2-bc97-437f-b95b-4bc1efe65b0e', 'businesses', '20e382e4-f9d9-4369-bb08-5b6016f7a091', 'DELETE', '{"id": "20e382e4-f9d9-4369-bb08-5b6016f7a091", "city": "Auckland ", "name": "Zeena Khan Coaching ", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": true, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": null, "featured": true, "industry": "Professional Services", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771900754213.jpg", "verified": true, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771900760675.png", "claimed_at": "2026-02-26T22:33:27.633401+00:00", "claimed_by": "system", "created_at": "2026-01-17T23:14:01.458139+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-24T02:39:28.186094+00:00", "description": "Zeena Khan Coaching stands at the intersection of modern leadership and cultural wisdom, offering a nuanced approach to professional development.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div>With a focus on empowering leaders to build agile and confident teams, Zeena''s coaching practice is particularly attuned to the complexities of the AI era. Her methodology is grounded in a strengths-based framework that encourages individuals to harness their unique capabilities while remaining culturally aware.<span style=\"font-family: Inter, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: Inter, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: Inter, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal;\">Zeena Khan brings a wealth of experience to her coaching engagements, drawing from her own heritage and understanding of diverse cultural perspectives. This blend of insight ensures that her clients are not only prepared to meet the challenges of today''s fast-paced business environment but are also equipped to lead with empathy and respect for the diverse backgrounds within their teams.&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: Inter, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-family: Inter, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal;\">At the core of Zeena''s practice is the belief that true leadership is about fostering an environment where all team members can thrive. By emphasizing cultural awareness and personal strengths, she helps leaders create workplaces that are both innovative and inclusive. Zeena Khan Coaching is dedicated to nurturing leadership that is as dynamic as the world around us, with a commitment to guiding professionals towards their highest potential.</span></div>", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Zeena Khan ", "created_date": "2026-01-17", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@ZeenaKhanCoaching ", "youtube": "https://youtube.com/@Adaptability Advantage ", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/ZeenaKhanCoaching "}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "hello@zeenakhan.com", "contact_phone": "021364881", "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://www.zeenakhan.com", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Fijian", "short_description": "Empowering leaders to foster agile, confident teams in the AI era.", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-26 22:41:19.95485+00'),
