afted solutions designed to last. Each project is approached with a focus on durability, functionality, and clean, professional finishes, ensuring results that are both practical and visually appealing.</p><p><br></p>\n<p>Known throughout Auckland for their strong work ethic, clear communication, and fair, competitive pricing, the team works closely with clients to make every build a collaborative and stress-free experience. Client ideas are respected and combined with expert guidance to achieve outcomes that balance vision with craftsmanship.</p><p><br></p>\n<p>More than just construction, Dan Kas Construction is about building long-term relationships and creating homes and structures that support families and communities. Whether upgrading an existing space or starting a new build, the team brings precision, reliability, and Pacific heart to every stage of the journey.</p>", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Dan Kas", "created_date": "2026-01-06", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@dan.kas7", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/dan.kas.construction"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "pacificmarketltd@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "021 0887 8365", "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://dan-kas-construction.nz", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Samoan", "short_description": "Built on Trust, Crafted by Community", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-26 22:51:12.876887+00'),
	('e9c1760e-56b3-4d5b-8f64-e85318e7c516', 'businesses', '5a9d097b-f9b8-40c0-8fa8-81173d741b6c', 'UPDATE', '{"id": "5a9d097b-f9b8-40c0-8fa8-81173d741b6c", "city": "Hamilton", "name": "Good Day Catering", "status": "active", "suburb": "Frankton", "address": "124 Commerce St, Frankton", "claimed": true, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": "d5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4", "featured": true, "industry": "Food & Agriculture", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771895347748.jpg", "verified": true, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771895339394.png", "claimed_at": "2026-02-26T22:33:27.633401+00:00", "claimed_by": "system", "created_at": "2025-12-15T20:47:33.428856+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-24T01:09:14.319904+00:00", "description": "<p><strong>Good-Day Catering</strong> is a Hamilton-based Pacific catering business proudly serving fresh, authentic Polynesian food for community gatherings, church events, pop-ups, and special occasions.</p><p><br></p>\n<p>Rooted in service and connection, Good-Day Catering is known for generous portions, traditional flavours, and food made with care — whether it’s for a church function, cultural celebration, or local market pop-up. Every dish is prepared with love, respect for culture, and a strong sense of community.</p><p><br></p>\n<p>From beautifully presented desserts to hearty Pacific favourites, Good-Day Catering brings people together through food that feels like home.</p>", "postal_code": "3204", "contact_name": "Liesl Laulu", "created_date": "2025-12-15", "social_links": {"facebook": "https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=61551654938620", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/goodday_catering"}, "state_region": "North Island", "contact_email": "liesl.laulu@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "0210796359", "business_hours": "Tuesday to Friday 11am-5pm \nSaturday 9am-3pm", "contact_website": null, "lang