ions designed to last. Each project is approached with a focus on durability, functionality, and clean, professional finishes, ensuring results that are both practical and visually appealing.\r\n\r\nKnown throughout Auckland for their strong work ethic, clear communication, and fair, competitive pricing, the team works closely with clients to make every build a collaborative and stress-free experience. Client ideas are respected and combined with expert guidance to achieve outcomes that balance vision with craftsmanship.\r\n\r\nMore than just construction, Dan Kas Construction is about building long-term relationships and creating homes and structures that support families and communities. Whether upgrading an existing space or starting a new build, the team brings precision, reliability, and Pacific heart to every stage of the journey.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Dan Kas", "created_date": "2026-01-06", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@dan.kas7", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/dan.kas.construction"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "pacificmarketltd@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "021 0887 8365", "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://dan-kas-construction.nz", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Samoan", "short_description": "Built on Trust, Crafted by Community", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-27 04:40:35.250108+00'),
