fe. Starting small and working with minimal materials, I began handcrafting Sei with love, care, and intention. What started as a simple creative outlet has grown into a heartfelt small business rooted in culture, creativity, and passion.\r\n\r\nAnarra Alofa is a reflection of my journey — as a mother, a Samoan woman, and a creator — and a celebration of the beauty we carry and share through our culture.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Sharon Naseri", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@anarraalofa2020", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/silaumea.ieru", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/anarraalofa2125"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "sharonnaseri@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "+64212170344", "business_hours": "Monday-Friday 9am-5pm", "contact_website": null, "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Samoan", "short_description": "Elevate your style with beautifully crafted Sei''s for every occasion at Anarra Alofa.", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-27 22:29:10.159879+00'),
