 is to offer enriching educational experiences that connect cultures and unlock global opportunities.\r\n\r\nJoin us, and let''s embark on a new learning adventure together.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Daniel Maine", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {}, "state_region": "Auckland", "contact_email": "travel@danielmaine.com", "contact_phone": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": null, "languages_spoken": ["English", "French", "Tahitian"], "cultural_identity": "Tahitian, Cook Island", "short_description": "Destination Management, Travel Consulting & Professional Services", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-27 23:23:47.549036+00'),
