l finishes, ensuring results that are both practical and visually appealing.\r\n\r\nKnown throughout Auckland for their strong work ethic, clear communication, and fair, competitive pricing, the team works closely with clients to make every build a collaborative and stress-free experience. Client ideas are respected and combined with expert guidance to achieve outcomes that balance vision with craftsmanship.\r\n\r\nMore than just construction, Dan Kas Construction is about building long-term relationships and creating homes and structures that support families and communities. Whether upgrading an existing space or starting a new build, the team brings precision, reliability, and Pacific heart to every stage of the journey.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Dan Kas", "created_date": "2026-01-06", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@dan.kas7", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/dan.kas.construction"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "pacificmarketltd@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "021 0887 8365", "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://dan-kas-construction.nz", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Samoan", "short_description": "Built on Trust, Crafted by Community", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-27 23:23:47.549036+00'),
	('fc393b11-4634-4b79-88ad-aeea73d867d0', 'businesses', '847bde54-f369-40c3-a22b-a4d045850982', 'UPDATE', '{"id": "847bde54-f369-40c3-a22b-a4d045850982", "city": "Auckland", "name": "Paulo Mauia", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": true, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": "d5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4", "industry": "Arts & Culture", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771898295405.jpg", "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771898286727.jpg", "claimed_at": "2026-02-26T22:33:27.633401+00:00", "claimed_by": "system", "created_at": "2025-12-17T05:28:29.873448+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-27T04:40:35.250108+00:00", "description": "Arts Finest Tattoo Shop, owned and led by Paulo Mauia, is a respected Samoan tattoo studio known for delivering finely detailed, culturally grounded tattoo work with skill, care, and integrity.\r\n\r\nSpecialising in Samoan and Polynesian tattoo designs, Paulo brings years of experience and a deep understanding of traditional patterns, symbolism, and placement. Each piece is carefully crafted to reflect identity, story, and cultural pride — whether through bold traditional work, custom designs, or finely executed modern pieces.\r\n\r\nArts Finest Tattoo Shop is more than a place to get tattooed; it is a space where art, heritage, and craftsmanship come together. With a strong reputation across Samoa and New Zealand — and expanding to Australia from January 2026 — the studio continues to serve clients who value authenticity, cultural respect, and high-quality tattooing.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Paulo Mauia", "created_date": "2025-12-17", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@paulomauia", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=100060918442844", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/paulomauia_tattoo"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "pau