lakai.com", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Samoan, Ireland", "short_description": "Speaker | Author | Podcast Host | Holistic Trauma & Elevation Coach | Conscious Relationship Work | Trauma-Informed Leadership & Mindset Integration", "subscription_tier": "featured", "stripe_customer_id": null}', '{"id": "09938336-c963-488a-9c0f-a387893bc13a", "city": "Auckland", "name": "Angela Malakai | The HONESTea", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": true, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": "d5cf35f3-321d-4fb1-9a68-9e16cab473e4", "industry": "Consulting & Professional Services", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771894190853.png", "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771894004538.jpg", "claimed_at": "2026-02-26T21:10:10.394806+00:00", "claimed_by": "system", "created_at": "2025-12-15T02:51:48.311365+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-27T23:23:47.549036+00:00", "description": "About The HONESTea\r\n\r\nThe HONESTea is where real conversations finally happen.\r\n\r\nHosted by Angela Malakai — Speaker, Author, and Holistic Trauma Coach — this podcast is built on truth, voice, and lived experience.\r\n\r\nThis is more than a podcast; it''s the foundation of a speaking platform rooted in honesty, healing, and authentic human connection.\r\n\r\nWe pour the tea that matters — the trauma tea, the growth tea, the spiritual tea, the identity tea, and everything in between.\r\n\r\nIt''s a space for cycle-breakers, leaders, deep feelers, and those who know they were made for more.\r\n\r\n🎙 HONESTea Podcast — Available to watch on YouTube.", "postal_code": null, "contact_name": "Angela (Ange) Malakai", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"youtube": "https://youtube.com/@angelamalakai", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/TheHONESTea", "linkedin": "https://linkedin.com/in/angela-malakai", "instagram": "h