ix, et vous lui donnez vie avec la peinture.\r\n🎨 Créez Votre Propre Motif (4h) — Concevez et peignez votre pareo de A à Z.\r\n\r\nTout le matériel est fourni — il vous suffit d''apporter votre créativité et vous repartirez avec un pareo unique, réalisé de vos propres mains. Une expérience", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "l-ame-du-pareu-by-vai-ohani", "contact_name": "Vaihere Pito", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@vaiohani", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/100046471642888", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/pareubyvaiohani.00"}, "state_region": "Ils Sous Le Vent", "contact_email": "lornapitovai@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "+689 87376668", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": null, "languages_spoken": ["English", "French", "Tahitian"], "cultural_identity": "Tahitian", "short_description": "A hands-on pareu painting experience in Raiatea", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', '{"id": "a1fb7177-900d-41f8-b635-c155a16c2e43", "city": "Raiatea", "name": "L''ame Du Pareu by Vai''ohani", "status": "active", "suburb": "Tumaraa", "address": "PK30.9 C/mer - Motu Nuutere", "claimed": false, "country": "French Polynesia", "user_id": null, "industry": "Arts & Culture", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771896719956.jpg", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771896711215.jpg", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2025-11-27T07:23:16.513022+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-03-02T19:52:50.688351+00:00", "description": "Discover the magic of pareo art with Vaihere in beautiful Raiatea. In this hands-on workshop, you''ll learn the traditional craft of painting your own pareo, using colours and patterns that reflect your personal story.\r\n\r\nChoose from three experience levels:\r\n🎨 Chi