urally aware.\r\n\r\nZeena Khan brings a wealth of experience to her coaching engagements, drawing from her own heritage and understanding of diverse cultural perspectives. This blend of insight ensures that her clients are not only prepared to meet the challenges of today''s fast-paced business environment but are also equipped to lead with empathy and respect for the diverse backgrounds within their teams.\r\n\r\nAt the core of Zeena''s practice is the belief that true leadership is about fostering an environment where all team members can thrive. By emphasizing cultural awareness and personal strengths, she helps leaders create workplaces that are both innovative and inclusive. Zeena Khan Coaching is dedicated to nurturing leadership that is as dynamic as the world around us, with a commitment to guiding professionals towards their highest potential.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "zeena-khan-coaching", "contact_name": "Zeena Khan", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@ZeenaKhanCoaching", "youtube": "https://youtube.com/@Adaptability Advantage", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/ZeenaKhanCoaching"}, "state_region": "North Island", "contact_email": "hello@zeenakhan.com", "contact_phone": "021364881", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://www.zeenakhan.com", "languages_spoken": ["Hindi"], "cultural_identity": "Fiji, China, India", "short_description": "Empowering leaders to foster agile, confident teams in the AI era.", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-02 19:55:13.415791+00'),
	('f08d2c33-901d-418a-8eb7-3fd8920c6662', 'businesses', '20b54ac1-50ae-4475-89ef-b50569505408', 'UPDATE', '{"id": "20b54ac1-50ae-4475-89ef-b50569505408", "city": "New Zealand", "name": "M.Steven", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": false, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": null, "industry": "Arts & Culture", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771896978917.jpeg", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771896973343.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2025-12-14T08:18:01.195186+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-02-28T02:28:45.479033+00:00", "description": "This artist brings worlds to life through intricate, hand-drawn line work, creating pieces that feel both deeply personal and endlessly expansive. Every artwork is built stroke by stroke — layering symbols, creatures, and flowing forms that invite the viewer to slow down and discover something new each time they look.\r\n\r\nInspired by storytelling, movement, and the complexity of lived experience, their work blends fine detail with raw expression. Using acrylic paint and acrylic pen alongside traditional drawing tools, each piece carries its own rhythm — reflecting patience, discipline, and a deep respect for the creative process.\r\n\r\nBeyond visual art, this same care and creativity extend into handcrafted desserts and custom celebration cakes, including wedding and birthday designs. Whether expressed on paper, canvas, or through edible art, the artist approaches every creation with the same intention: balance, beauty, and meaning.\r\n\r\nThese works are never rushed — they are thoughtfully crafted, allowing ideas to unfold naturally. The result is a body of work that feels alive and grounded, celebrating creativity as a form of meditation, expression, and connection across many mediums.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "m-steven", "contact_name": "Mario Steven", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@m.stevenfjrot23"}, "state_region": "New Zealand", "contact_email": "mariosteven75@yahoo.co.nz", "contact_phone": null, "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": null, "languages_spoken": ["Fijian", "Rotuman", "Hindi", "Te Reo Māori (basic)"], "cultural_identity": "Fijian, Italy", "short_description": "Stories in Every Intricate Stroke & Sweet Creation", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', '{"id": "20b54ac1-50ae-4475-89ef-b50569505408", "city": "New Zealand", "name": "M.Steven", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": false, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": null, "industry": "Arts & Culture", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logo_1771896978917.jpeg", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banner_1771896973343.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2025-12-14T08:18:01.195186+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-03-02T19:55:13.415791+00:00", "description": "This artist brings worlds to life through intricate, hand-drawn line work, creating pieces that feel both deeply personal and endlessly expansive. Every artwork is built stroke by stroke — layering symbols, creatures, and flowing forms that invite the viewer to slow down and discover something new each time they look.\r\n\r\nInspired by storytelling, movement, and the complexity of lived experience, their work blends fine detail with raw expression. Using acrylic paint and acrylic pen alongside traditional drawing tools, each piece carries its own rhythm — reflecting patience, discipline, and a deep respect for the creative process.\r\n\r\nBeyond visual art, this same care and creativity extend into handcrafted desserts and custom celebration cakes, including wedding and birthday designs. Whether expressed on paper, canvas, or through edible art, the artist approaches every creation with the same intention: balance, beauty, and meaning.\r\n\r\nThese works are never rushed — they are thoughtfully crafted, allowing ideas to unfold naturally. The result is a body of work that feels alive and grounded, celebrating creativity as a form of meditation, expression, and connection across many mediums.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "m-steven", "contact_name": "Mario Steven", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@m.stevenfjrot23"}, "state_region": "New Zealand", "contact_email": "mariosteven75@yahoo.co.nz", "contact_phone": null, "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": null, "languages_spoken": ["Fijian", "Rotuman", "Hindi", "Te Reo Māori (basic)"], "cultural_identity": "Fiji, Italy", "short_description": "Stories in Every Intricate Stroke & Sweet Creation", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-02 19:55:13.415791+00'),
