.\r\n\r\nZeena Khan brings a wealth of experience to her coaching engagements, drawing from her own heritage and understanding of diverse cultural perspectives. This blend of insight ensures that her clients are not only prepared to meet the challenges of today''s fast-paced business environment but are also equipped to lead with empathy and respect for the diverse backgrounds within their teams.\r\n\r\nAt the core of Zeena''s practice is the belief that true leadership is about fostering an environment where all team members can thrive. By emphasizing cultural awareness and personal strengths, she helps leaders create workplaces that are both innovative and inclusive. Zeena Khan Coaching is dedicated to nurturing leadership that is as dynamic as the world around us, with a commitment to guiding professionals towards their highest potential.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "zeena-khan-coaching", "contact_name": "Zeena Khan", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@ZeenaKhanCoaching", "youtube": "https://youtube.com/@Adaptability Advantage", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/ZeenaKhanCoaching"}, "state_region": "North Island", "contact_email": "hello@zeenakhan.com", "contact_phone": "021364881", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://www.zeenakhan.com", "languages_spoken": ["Hindi"], "cultural_identity": "Fiji, China, India", "short_description": "Empowering leaders to foster agile, confident teams in the AI era.", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-03 05:58:53.043436+00'),
