, including wedding and birthday designs. Whether expressed on paper, canvas, or through edible art, the artist approaches every creation with the same intention: balance, beauty, and meaning.\r\n\r\nThese works are never rushed — they are thoughtfully crafted, allowing ideas to unfold naturally. The result is a body of work that feels alive and grounded, celebrating creativity as a form of meditation, expression, and connection across many mediums.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "m-steven", "contact_name": "Mario Steven", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@m.stevenfjrot23"}, "state_region": "New Zealand", "contact_email": "mariosteven75@yahoo.co.nz", "contact_phone": null, "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": null, "languages_spoken": ["Fijian", "Rotuman", "Hindi", "Te Reo Māori (basic)"], "cultural_identity": "Fiji, Italy", "short_description": "Stories in Every Intricate Stroke & Sweet Creation", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-03 06:09:11.046545+00'),
