 team brings precision, reliability, and Pacific heart to every stage of the journey.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "dan-kas-construction", "contact_name": "Dan Kas", "created_date": "2026-01-06", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@dan.kas7", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/dan.kas.construction"}, "state_region": null, "contact_email": "pacificmarketltd@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "021 0887 8365", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://dan-kas-construction.nz", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Samoa", "short_description": "Built on Trust, Crafted by Community", "subscription_tier": "featured_plus", "stripe_customer_id": null}', '{"id": "f9ba8226-cffa-44af-9481-0bcfbd86c100", "city": "Auckland", "name": "DAN KAS Construction", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": false, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": null, "industry": "Construction & Trades", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/dankas.png", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Dan%20Kas.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2026-01-06T18:27:30.26066+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-03-03T06:13:06.643013+00:00", "description": "Dan Kas Construction is an Auckland-based building company built on hard work, attention to detail, and a genuine commitment to quality workmanship. Led by a skilled Samoan crew, the team brings values of service, care, and collective strength into every project, delivering work with integrity and pride.\r\n\r\nSpecialising in new builds, renovations, decking, fencing, recladding, and general maintenance, Dan Kas Construction provides reliable, well-crafted solutions designed to last. Each project is approached with a focus on durability, functionality, and clean, professional finishes, ensuring 