lities while remaining culturally aware.\r\n\r\nZeena Khan brings a wealth of experience to her coaching engagements, drawing from her own heritage and understanding of diverse cultural perspectives. This blend of insight ensures that her clients are not only prepared to meet the challenges of today''s fast-paced business environment but are also equipped to lead with empathy and respect for the diverse backgrounds within their teams.\r\n\r\nAt the core of Zeena''s practice is the belief that true leadership is about fostering an environment where all team members can thrive. By emphasizing cultural awareness and personal strengths, she helps leaders create workplaces that are both innovative and inclusive. Zeena Khan Coaching is dedicated to nurturing leadership that is as dynamic as the world around us, with a commitment to guiding professionals towards their highest potential.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "zeena-khan-coaching", "contact_name": "Zeena Khan", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"tiktok": "https://tiktok.com/@ZeenaKhanCoaching", "youtube": "https://youtube.com/@Adaptability Advantage", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/ZeenaKhanCoaching"}, "state_region": "North Island", "contact_email": "hello@zeenakhan.com", "contact_phone": "021364881", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://www.zeenakhan.com", "visibility_tier": "homepage", "languages_spoken": ["Hindi", "English"], "cultural_identity": "Fiji, China, India", "homepage_featured": true, "short_description": "Empowering leaders to foster agile, confident teams in the AI era.", "subscription_tier": "verified", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00'),
	('800e6d17-540b-42bd-9896-d93c72558016', 'businesses', 'c9fc68e6-da63-4def-9d0b-13991ddc3926', 'UPDATE', '{"id": "c9fc68e6-da63-4def-9d0b-13991ddc3926", "city": "Auckland", "name": "Te Mauri o te Makawe", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": false, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": null, "industry": "Health & Wellness", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/temauri.jpg", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Te%20Mauri.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2025-12-01T08:40:49.119488+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-03-05T02:32:21.595222+00:00", "description": "Nuku te manaaki, nuku te manaaki, ka ora ai te iwi.\r\nWith your support and my support, our community will thrive.\r\n\r\nMy name is Iesha Te-Iho. I am a qualified barber, creative, and proud Waiuku local. My journey here was not a straight line — but every challenge sharpened my purpose and showed me that barbering could be more than a trade. It could be a doorway to healing.\r\n\r\nFrom that understanding, Te Mauri o te Makawe: The Koha Manawa was born.\r\n\r\nThis kaupapa delivers professional grooming and braiding through a mobile service, reaching people and places often overlooked — hospices, spinal units, rehabilitation centres, and rural communities where transport and access are barriers. But this work is about far more than hair.\r\n\r\nThrough whakahoki te tapu, hair is treated with care and respectfully returned to Papatūānuku using traditional tikanga — uku (clay), harakeke (flax), and korowai — protecting the mana of our whānau. Alongside this, kōrero is shared and recorded, preserving the voices, stories, and heartbeat of the community.\r\n\r\nThis kaupapa began with one chair and one set of tools, but the vision is a Waka Wānanga — a collective of skilled creatives travelling across Aotearoa and beyond, delivering workshops, teaching tikanga, uplifting hauora, and restoring identity through creativity.\r\n\r\nAt its heart, this is about legacy. About building something that lasts — not just 100 years, but for generations — by caring for people, culture, and community, together.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "te-mauri-o-te-makawe", "contact_name": "Iesha Rawinia", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"facebook": "https://facebook.com/TeKohaManawa", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/tekohamanawa"}, "state_region": "Auckland", "contact_email": "hairwithesha@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "02102965229", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://msha.ke/beauty_withinyou", "visibility_tier": "none", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Cook Islands, New Zealand Māori", "homepage_featured": true, "short_description": "Any Style. Any Hair. Any Where.", "subscription_tier": "verified", "stripe_customer_id": null}', '{"id": "c9fc68e6-da63-4def-9d0b-13991ddc3926", "city": "Auckland", "name": "Te Mauri o te Makawe", "status": "active", "suburb": null, "address": null, "claimed": false, "country": "New Zealand", "user_id": null, "industry": "Health & Wellness", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/temauri.jpg", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Te%20Mauri.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2025-12-01T08:40:49.119488+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-03-05T02:35:18.829614+00:00", "description": "Nuku te manaaki, nuku te manaaki, ka ora ai te iwi.\r\nWith your support and my support, our community will thrive.\r\n\r\nMy name is Iesha Te-Iho. I am a qualified barber, creative, and proud Waiuku local. My journey here was not a straight line — but every challenge sharpened my purpose and showed me that barbering could be more than a trade. It could be a doorway to healing.\r\n\r\nFrom that understanding, Te Mauri o te Makawe: The Koha Manawa was born.\r\n\r\nThis kaupapa delivers professional grooming and braiding through a mobile service, reaching people and places often overlooked — hospices, spinal units, rehabilitation centres, and rural communities where transport and access are barriers. But this work is about far more than hair.\r\n\r\nThrough whakahoki te tapu, hair is treated with care and respectfully returned to Papatūānuku using traditional tikanga — uku (clay), harakeke (flax), and korowai — protecting the mana of our whānau. Alongside this, kōrero is shared and recorded, preserving the voices, stories, and heartbeat of the community.\r\n\r\nThis kaupapa began with one chair and one set of tools, but the vision is a Waka Wānanga — a collective of skilled creatives travelling across Aotearoa and beyond, delivering workshops, teaching tikanga, uplifting hauora, and restoring identity through creativity.\r\n\r\nAt its heart, this is about legacy. About building something that lasts — not just 100 years, but for generations — by caring for people, culture, and community, together.", "postal_code": null, "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "te-mauri-o-te-makawe", "contact_name": "Iesha Rawinia", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"facebook": "https://facebook.com/TeKohaManawa", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/tekohamanawa"}, "state_region": "Auckland", "contact_email": "hairwithesha@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "02102965229", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://msha.ke/beauty_withinyou", "visibility_tier": "homepage", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": "Cook Islands, New Zealand Māori", "homepage_featured": true, "short_description": "Any Style. Any Hair. Any Where.", "subscription_tier": "verified", "stripe_customer_id": null}', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-05 02:35:18.829614+00'),
	('bcdee755-2d43-45af-a985-2f846d426ca3', 'businesses', 'c4530355-c5fb-47fb-ac89-07574831f9e7', 'UPDATE', '{"id": "c4530355-c5fb-47fb-ac89-07574831f9e7", "city": "Naples", "name": "Avalon Wellness and Performance", "status": "active", "suburb": "Naples", "address": "10661 Airport Pulling Road N #10, Naples FL 34109", "claimed": false, "country": "United States", "user_id": null, "industry": "Health & Wellness", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/avalon.jpg", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Avalon.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2026-01-08T00:54:56.222151+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-03-05T02:32:21.595222+00:00", "description": "Avalon Wellness & Performance is a holistic health clinic dedicated to helping people move better, feel stronger, and live with greater ease and confidence. Through personalised, hands-on care, Avalon supports recovery, long-term wellness, and peak physical performance.\r\n\r\nThe clinic takes an integrative approach to treatment, combining techniques such as Active Release Technique (ART), Osteopathic Manual Therapy, Cranial Sacral Therapy, and therapeutic massage. Each session is tailored to the individual, addressing not only symptoms but the underlying causes of pain, tension, and movement restrictions.\r\n\r\nAt Avalon, the body is viewed as a connected system. Treatment plans are developed through careful assessment and collaboration, ensuring care aligns with each client''s goals — whether that''s injury recovery, pain management, improved mobility, or enhanced athletic performance.\r\n\r\nAvalon Wellness & Performance provides a calm, professional environment where expertise and compassion come together. From deep tissue and mobility-focused work to gentle therapies that support nervous system balance and stress relief, every session is delivered with intention and care.\r\n\r\nMore than treatment, Avalon empowers clients with the tools, support, and knowledge needed to maintain their wellbeing long after their session ends — helping them move forward feeling stronger, balanced, and supported.", "postal_code": "34109", "proof_links": null, "shop_handle": "avalon-wellness-and-performance", "contact_name": "Avalon Wellness Performance", "created_date": "2026-02-26", "social_links": {"twitter": "https://twitter.com/WellnessAvalon", "facebook": "https://facebook.com/avalonwellnessandperformance", "instagram": "https://instagram.com/avalonwellnessandperformance"}, "state_region": "FL", "contact_email": "avalonwellnessperformance@gmail.com", "contact_phone": "+632394274697", "owner_user_id": null, "business_hours": null, "contact_website": "https://www.avalonwellnessandperformance.com/", "visibility_tier": "none", "languages_spoken": ["English"], "cultural_identity": null, "homepage_featured": true, "short_description": "Move Better. Feel Better. Live Better.", "subscription_tier": "verified", "stripe_customer_id": null}', '{"id": "c4530355-c5fb-47fb-ac89-07574831f9e7", "city": "Naples", "name": "Avalon Wellness and Performance", "status": "active", "suburb": "Naples", "address": "10661 Airport Pulling Road N #10, Naples FL 34109", "claimed": false, "country": "United States", "user_id": null, "industry": "Health & Wellness", "logo_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/logos/avalon.jpg", "verified": false, "banner_url": "https://mnmisjprswpuvcojnbip.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/admin-listings/banners/Avalon.png", "claimed_at": null, "claimed_by": null, "created_at": "2026-01-08T00:54:56.222151+00:00", "updated_at": "2026-03-05T02:35:18.829614+00:00", "description": "Avalon Wellness & Performance is a holistic health clinic dedicated to helping people move better, feel stronger, and live with greater ease and confidence. Through personalised, hands-on care, Avalon 